

	 
      Take another look at me  Oh breaker of my heart  Take a look and you will see  How beautiful you are  Even when I walk away  I could not go very far  Before the child in me would say  Home is where you are   In the tapestry of time  I cannot imagine where  I could find someone as kind  On the ground or in the air  I have heard that angels fly  And they never show their face  So I suppose that from the sky  One landed in your place  -Bebo Norman, "Where You Are"
    
